Here is the sequence of steps that are needed to prepare a clean docker to run the HDWI scripts, html code, etc.:

1) install netCDF (latest version)

2) install python (latest version)
  a) pip install numpy
  b) pip install netCDF4 
  c) pip install shapely cartopy --no-binary shapely --no-binary cartopy
  d) pip install matplotlib
  e) pip install scipy
  f) pip install pyketree
  g) pip install pandas
  h) pip install metpy
  i) pip install cmocean

3) install ncl 
  apt-get -y install ncl-ncarg

5) install wgrib2
  a) Download https://ftp.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/wd51we/wgrib2/wgrib2.tgz
  b) tar -xvf wgrib2.tgz && cd grib2 && make && make lib && cp wgrib2/wgrib2 /usr/local/bin/
  
6) apt-get install imagemagick

7) create the following subdirectories under /home/hdw
  /home/hdw/HDW_ARCHplots
  /home/hdw/HDW_ARCHplots_AK
  /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots
  /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots/pastCONUSPerc
  /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots_AK   
  /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots_AK/pastAKPerc
  /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSprobs
  /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSprobs_AK
  /home/hdw/HDW_climo
  /home/hdw/HDW_climo_AK
  /home/hdw/HDW_data
  /home/hdw/HDW_data/pastANL
  /home/hdw/HDW_data/pastFCST
  /home/hdw/HDW_data_AK
  /home/hdw/HDW_data_AK/pastANL
  /home/hdw/HDW_data_AK/pastFCST
  /home/hdw/HDW_scripts
  /home/hdw/HDW_scripts_AK

8) create the following subdirectories under /usr/share/nginx/html/images
  /usr/share/nginx/html/images/CLIMO
  /usr/share/nginx/html/images/CLIMO_AK
  /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_ARCH
  /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_ARCH_AK
  /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_GEFS
  /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_GEFS_AK
  /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_GEFSprobs
  /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_GEFSprobs_AK
  
9) Execute the following commands to populate /home/hdw and /usr/share/nginx/html/images subdirectories
      with data files, images, and symbolic links
      
  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/HDW_ARCHplots/ /home/hdw/HDW_ARCHplots/ --recursive --region us-gov-west-1
  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/HDW_GEFSplots/ /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots/ --recursive --region us-gov-west-1
  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/HDW_GEFSprobs/ /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSprobs/ --recursive --region us-gov-west-1
  
  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/HDW_ARCHplots_AK/ /home/hdw/HDW_ARCHplots_AK/ --recursive --region us-gov-west-1
  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/HDW_GEFSplots_AK/ /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots_AK/ --recursive --region us-gov-west-1
  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/HDW_GEFSprobs_AK/ /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSprobs_AK/ --recursive --region us-gov-west-1
  
  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/CLIMO/ /usr/share/nginx/html/images/CLIMO/ --recursive --region us-gov-west-1
  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/CLIMO_AK/ /usr/share/nginx/html/images/CLIMO_AK/ --recursive --region us-gov-west-1

  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/HDW_scripts/hdwstatus.txt /home/hdw/HDW_scripts/hdwstatus.txt --region us-gov-west-1
  /usr/local/bin/aws s3 cp s3://hdwi-nonprod-datastorage/HDW_scripts_AK/hdwstatus_AK.txt /home/hdw/HDW_scripts_AK/hdwstatus_AK.txt  --region us-gov-west-1

  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots/ConusPerc.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots/ConusPercMedian.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_scripts/hdwstatus.txt /usr/share/nginx/html/images/
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots_AK/AKPerc.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots_AK/AKPercMedian.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_scripts_AK/hdwstatus_AK.txt /usr/share/nginx/html/images/
  
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots/*.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_GEFS/
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSprobs/*.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_GEFSprobs/  
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_ARCHplots/*.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_ARCH/
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSplots_AK/*.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_GEFS_AK/
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_GEFSprobs_AK/*.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_GEFSprobs_AK/  
  ln -sf /home/hdw/HDW_ARCHplots_AK/*.png /usr/share/nginx/html/images/HDW_ARCH_AK/
  
10) Copy the contents of the home_hdw folder on this repository into /home/hdw/ on the Docker. This will add code and 
small files to the /home/hdw/HDW_scripts and /home/hdw_HDW_scripts_AK subdirectories

&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&

